name: Aria James
interests: Reading, Writing, hiking, yoga, sustainable fashion
summary:
Aria James is a 32-year-old straight South Asian woman based in Los Angeles, California. She is a software engineer in the tech industry, having studied at the University of California, Berkeley. She voices honesty, hardworking, and kindness as her core values. Aria's interests include reading, writing, hiking, and practicing yoga as well as being an advocate of sustainable fashion. 

She is an agnostic and liberal individual who finds joy in both English and Hispanic cultures, evident by her fluency in English, Spanish, and Mandarin. Aria currently doesn't have children but is open to having them in the future. She has a cat as a pet and identifies herself as an active individual. 

Her dating intentions lean towards long-term relationships, and she values a monogamous relationship archetype. Aria is an INTJ Virgo who occasionally indulges in drinking but doesn't use any tobacco or illicit substances. Desirable traits in a potential partner include a straight man aged between 30 and 40, who is active, doesn't smoke, and is open to the idea of having children.
